    "dd1362": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "lang": "lg-nolan",
        "value": "<p>The RDF schema is defined inside the Ontology below the External Ontologies term (dd1270), every schema need to be referenced by the specific tld, ex: for Nomisma ontology is used numisdata tld.</p><p></p><p>This tool use the component_iri data to get the enter point into the RDF graph.</p><p></p><p>Data communication and transformation is done through RDF schema relationships and associated components.</p>"
      }
    ],
